@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_pwmtwr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.43 / v0 + 0.89)) - (0.46 + (tmp + 0.52 / v1 + 0.79)))
    v2 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.84 * tmp + 0.12)) - (0.02 * (v0 + 0.30 - tmp + 0.26)))
    tmp = (v2 - (v2 + wp.sin(v0 + 0.04)))
    v1 = 0.04
    v0 = wp.exp(0.45)
    v0 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
